highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Germany. “Golden” is the highest at #12.
“Bam Bam” by Banfy and Sheridan is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Germany at #3.
“Als du gingst - edit” by Contec and Lina Maly has been on Viral Songs Germany the longest, at 119 days straight.
“Du bist wie” by Laurenz Nikolaus is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Germany, up 8 spots at #43.
